text: Jhonnatan Botero Villegas (born 27 April 1992) is a Colombian mountain bike racer. He rode at the cross-country event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Colombian male cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Colombia
